    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "AIRCAL\nSYSTEM TIMETABLE\nEffective July 1, 1982\nEXPANDED SUMMER SERVICE\nVAFLEX\n103\nNOW SERVING BURBANK",
      "AIRCAL\nNow were\nserving Burbank-\nGlendale-\nPasadena\nAirport — the\nmost convenient airport for the San\nFernando Valley, Hollywood, down-\ntown Los Angeles and Burbank-\nwhich happens to be next door to\nworld-famous Universal Studios\nTour® Now you can enjoy that AirCal\nstyle, flying to and from Oakland, San\nJose, Sacramento, Seattle-lacoma\nand Burbank aboard a Super\nDC-9-80, the quietest jet in its class.\nAs on all our flights, you get\nthat special AirCal\ntreatment. Above the\nground and on the ground.\nWith schedules planned for your\nconvenience, not ours. One-stop\ncheck in. Seat selection on every\nflight and baggage that's more\noften waiting for you than the other\nway around. On AirCal, we make\nyou feel so special, you'll think\nyou're the only passenger.\nNow you have the conve-\nnience of flying AirCal from LAX,\nOntario, John Wayne Orange\nCounty and the Burbank-Glendale-\nPasadena Airport.\nUniversal Studios GlamorTram\nOfficial airline of Universal Studio's Tour.®"
    ],
